These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: coffee, fanta
Music-Genre: gospel, classical
Color: orange, azure
Food: kiwi, grapes
1. Food:grapes is on the left or right of Color:azure##3
2. Beverage:fanta is in an even position##4
3. Music-Genre:classical == Beverage:coffee##1
4. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | gospel   |
| Color         | azure | orange |
| Food     | kiwi | grapes    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
City: san-francisco, miami
Movie-Genre: action, documentary
Game: billiard, bridge
Color: purple, blue
1. Game:bridge is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:action == Color:blue##1
3. City:miami is on the right of Movie-Genre:documentary##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| City          | san-francisco     | miami |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Game           | bridge         | billiard     |
| Color     | purple   | blue    |

 #################################
 
