.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Game: domino, chess
Food: cabbage, strawberry
Hobby: woodworking, hiking
Sport: climbing, soccer
1. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
2. Food:strawberry is on the far left or far right##3
3. Game:chess == Food:cabbage##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Food:strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Game           | chess | domino    |
| Food   | cabbage       | strawberry |
| Hobby           | woodworking         | hiking    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

